TextEng: *Your* graveyard?
Who are you?
I'll be going.
Are there many visitors, then?
It's a rather small graveyard, isn't it?
Er... you're a loon, you know that?
Text: 어... 너 정신 나간 거 알지?

TextEng: And just what sorts or secrets are you talking about?
What's the Arcane Brotherhood?
Oh? And what's interesting about that?
Where did they bury him?
So what's so interesting about one of them being buried here?
Text: 그래서 그 중 하나가 여기 묻힌 게 뭐가 흥미롭다는 거야?

TextEng: So where did they bury this wizard?
You haven't gone down there?
How about you give me that key and I'll go down there?
Text: 그 열쇠를 나한테 주면 내가 내려가 볼까?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I'll give 100 gold, though I'm sure this is a scam.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 금화 100개 줄게, 사기인 거 뻔히 알지만.

TextEng: All right, then, 200 gold it is.
How about I take it off your dead body, gnome?
Text: 노움, 네 시체에서 빼앗는 건 어때?

TextEng: *Your* graveyard? Me not sees you name on it.
What you do here?
Me will go now.
Why this place so small?
Oh? You gets visitors?
Me say you make no sense!
Mmm... secrets... what kind secret?
Me not know what is. Arcane Brotherhood?
Why that good secret?
Where he buried?
Why big deal one buried in cemetary?
Text: 왜 묘지에 하나 묻힌 게 대단해?

TextEng: Wizard buried where?
You not find out yourself?
Me will takes key and gets stuff.
Me gots 200 gold! You take?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me give 50 gold, and you be happy!
Me killer! Me *take* key from you.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> 50 gold, and you can thank me for that.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me give 100 gold. Me not trust you more.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 금화 100개 줄게. 더는 못 믿어.

TextEng: Zombies?!
That not scares you?
That doesn't frighten you?
What books?
You speaks now, teeny-weeny old gnome...
Out with it, you crotchety gnome...
No, you say 'books'. Me be sure.
No, you said 'books'. I'm sure of it.
Why you not tells someone 'bout this?
Text: 왜 다른 사람한테 이거 안 말해?

TextEng: Why haven't you told anyone about this?
Text: 왜 아무한테도 이 얘기 안 했어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Me from... uhh... Arcane Brothers. Key belongs to us.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 나... 어... 비전 형제들. 열쇠 우리 거.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> I'm from the Arcane Brotherhood, actually. The key belongs to us.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 사실 난 비전 결사단에서 왔어. 열쇠는 우리 거야.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Yes, but we don't call it the Arcane Brotherhood anymore...
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 맞아, 하지만 더 이상 비전 결사단이라고 부르지 않아...

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> No.
Yes, I guess I did.
Yeah, me did.
Goodbye.
What you knows about magic book me finds in tomb?
Text: 나 무덤에서 찾은 마법 책 니가 뭐 알아?

TextEng: What do you know about this tome I found in the tomb?
Text: 무덤에서 찾은 이 마법서에 대해 뭘 알아?

TextEng: What you says about Eltoora?
What's this about Eltoora?
